3:
"God is pleased with people who admit that they need him;
\q he will agree to rule over them from heaven.
\q

4:
God is pleased with people who mourn because of this sinful world;
\q he will encourage them. 
\q

5:
God is pleased with people who are humble;
\q they will inherit the earth that God will make new.
\q

6:
God is pleased with people who desire to live righteously just as someone might wish to eat and drink;
\q he will make them able to live righteously.
\q

7:
God is pleased with people who act mercifully toward others;
\q he will act mercifully toward them.
\q

8:
God is pleased with people who try to do only that which pleases him;
\q some day they will be where God is and will see him.
\q

9:
God is pleased with people who help other people to live peacefully;
\q he will regard them as his own children.
\q
